  KEY OBSERVATION:
    QR: |QR·QR| = m (closed under multiplication!)
    Interval: |I·I| >> m (no multiplicative structure)
    QR: |QR+QR| = p-1 or p (forced large by sum-product)
    Interval: |I+I| ~ 2m = p-1 (arithmetic progression sumset)

